Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.26,0:00:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,60)\1c4B33D1\3c000000\bord3}剩余\N40天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半天搞定作业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的四十天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约等于一千小时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.32,0:00:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以无尽地玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何这两天艾露希也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换言之
