Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈  我现在出门买游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来四十天人间蒸发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但请您不要担心  就这样  拜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手  我的一千小时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来  跟客人打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马还记得吧  以前住我们隔壁的鲇川一家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马十年没见了  还记得我这个阿姨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太记得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理快看  是桂马
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理  都说是桂马了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁…来着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打游戏打游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:01:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  这几天都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到地狱开报告会了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一点玩游戏的时间都不给吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是给哥哥大人带的特产  针球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来有妹妹的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言难尽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫艾露希  您好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个玩具真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起  我家的孩子还是这么不礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}完全没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}…也许有点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  桂马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说不记得  太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  小学一年级时你俩不是同班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人都只拍到了半身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  印象中是有个扭扭捏捏的女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又好像没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的记忆真靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种场合就算忘记了也得说记得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这问题毫不重要  我要去买游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八月底再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的教育果然有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚探测器好像响了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十天  一千小时！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探测器响了就有申告的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免两个恶魔同时追捕同一对象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  暑假  你比任何女主角都更有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定驱魂跑进哥哥大人的青梅竹马身体里去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  竟敢妄称青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才不是青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:03:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换言之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fs20\bord0\fad(120,0)}Flag  壹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fs20\bord0}Flag  贰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fs20\bord0}Flag  叁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fs20\bord0}Flag  肆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fs20\bord0}Flag  伍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长期构建哥哥或弟弟这种恋人以下的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定过通往结局的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回忆中将要忘记一切的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换了截然不同的立场再会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才叫青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  那种似有似无的女人不是青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  游戏里的青梅竹马可是未来的结婚对象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要随便地设定这么重要的关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是神哥哥大人忘记了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都干了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  起码先道个歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能扪心自问一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱魂？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是抱着何等的决心踏进桂木家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你却一句「不记得」一笔带过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比这更伤人的话语了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没指望过你能帮助我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助？帮助是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不响了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是驱魂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟诺拉小姐为敌是很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追到这么远的地方来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条大鱼可不能放跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是明明白白地登记了负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好  接下来就轮到我们出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青梅竹马体内有驱魂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说那不是青梅竹马了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就申请负责了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要我出马吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这套路挺常见应该不难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是内向女孩的强烈愿望化为别的人格表现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没指望过你能帮助我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞岛学园
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的变化最大  跟十年前相比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上高中就别老是按泡沫包装纸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别  别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好担心天理的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄安娜  为什么要把他推下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以创造和他对话的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为天理在抵抗才显得这么奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你要我马上说出口我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理  我再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在被人追踪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前的我能力不够  必须要依靠他人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不能信任桂木桂马那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他简直就是钝感的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为桂马同学一定能帮助我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理的驱魂负责人被抢先登记了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责人是…诺拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在我的负责地区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  有其他人帮我解决啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  诺拉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再和桂木桂马说话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将思绪投入波浪之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能获得一时的安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你心灵的间隙  还是会一直残留
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心灵的间隙  就由我来填补吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将一切都交给我吧  来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就听听他说的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟医生问诊差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮  继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这些人就是狄安娜所说的… 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  我们是你的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心中现在住着一个叫驱魂的坏东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放任不管就会越来越强酿成大祸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要把他给淹死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将产生间隙的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用数倍的巨大欲望来填补的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱魂就会满溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要一万元的人就给他一百万
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要恋人的女性就给他男公关部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭受欺凌的人就给他复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的愿望是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的羽衣能够反映出人心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就简单了  喜欢和讨厌的二选一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是讨厌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就让这个男人吃点苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉  她不是两方面都说NO了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界憎恨比爱要来得更多更强大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都当成憎恨的话一般都没错的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正没有听她细细道来的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害  不愧是诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我可以杀了他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉以快速解决闻名  试过半天内就赶出了驱魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  失败次数也很多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还试过反过头来把驱魂养大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样子没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还试过抛下协力者  自己一个人赶出驱魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这做法实际上是禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这都是传闻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正已经和我无关…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底什么地方得罪你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹  待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着  通往光明未来的招待券哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公开处刑通知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心灵的间隙由我们来填补
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在海边公园  等着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏  游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥我要被绑着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次好像也能快速解决呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂  桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  还挺快的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹睁大眼睛看着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就让你憎恨的男人吃点苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就不恨桂马同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫描仪可不是这么说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这个男人你的心灵才会产生间隙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个间隙里面就躲着驱魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉  请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是我的协力者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协力者？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样  这家伙就是诺拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更有蹂躏的价值了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔复活后再收服可是禁止的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是原则上禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是绝对禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的协力者还不太成气候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是没办法才这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就留他一命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我要让他比死更难受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把这个男人最重要的东西给毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  你要做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心中最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学  我好想你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四妹  真的是小四妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于  来到结局的彼岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么愿望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非这就是那家伙所喜欢的女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把你最重要的东西给毁掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学是怎么看我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么问  说不出口啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你肯说的话  我也说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂…桂…桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎样  失去至爱的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读取
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读取读取读取读取读取…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读取
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁  到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死小四妹的到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为了煽情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者制造肤浅的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不动就把女主角杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有想过被你们杀掉的女主角是什么感受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把  小四妹还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心  好恶心  好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  天理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人漂亮地把那两人赶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让这个人来保护我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那种  像那种恶心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有活着的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把他杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行啊  诺拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是协力者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭档的恶魔也会一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露希也会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死就死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真随便
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要碰上这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剧院
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的话能躲起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要是被发现了就没地方可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是需要解决根本问题的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  为啥非得要我保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直这样放着不管会很危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺拉认为只要让哥哥大人吃苦头驱魂就会跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用别的驱魂来当作天理的驱魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后让其被诺拉抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后被发现了也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把我被她盯上的这个状态给解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我没有能替换的驱魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过白亚可能有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊明明是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我悠闲玩游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思议的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这个状况了还能这么冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是早知道会有这种事情发生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就多带几个备用电池出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前好像也在哪里发生过类似的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就剩下两个人了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是那种气氛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出一点勇气  天理这种时候就该…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这次逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你身上还留着驱魂那还是什么都没解决
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要依靠驱魂  自己想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱魂什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好像天理有问题似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能原谅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱魂就给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要依靠我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我之间有什么联系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也说了不记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…从来都没有忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂马同学  跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.73,0:22:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明都不是这里的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.29,0:22:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里面的路你认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.43,0:22:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我以前来过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和桂马同学一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.16,0:23:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那个时候也担心过电池的问题
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.00,0:23:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬头看看吧  夜空的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那颗星星和那颗星星和那颗星星连接在一起就成了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galge座了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那旁边的是美少女游戏座
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再旁边的就是恋爱模拟游戏座
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看起来很像但全部都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.52,0:23:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部连在一起成了消防车
